org.matsim.contrib.socnetgen.sna.graph

Interface GraphProjectionFactory<G2 extends Graph,V2 extends Vertex,E2 extends Edge,G extends GraphProjection<G2,V2,E2>,V extends VertexDecorator<V2>,E extends EdgeDecorator<E2>>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SampledGraphProjectionFactory, SocialSampledGraphProjectionFactory, SparseGraphProjectionFactory, SpatialSampledGraphProjectionFactory

    public interface GraphProjectionFactory<G2 extends Graph,V2 extends Vertex,E2 extends Edge,G extends GraphProjection<G2,V2,E2>,V extends VertexDecorator<V2>,E extends EdgeDecorator<E2>>
    A graph projection factory is responsible for instantiating new graph projections, vertex decorators and edge decorators. It does not handle the connectivity of vertices and edges.
    Author:
    illenberger
